summary: The Potter Twins and the Chamber of Secrets
title: The Potter Twins and the Chamber of Secrets
body:
When Aralynn Potter returns for her second year at Hogwarts, she must learn to cope with her new reality as The Girl Who Lived. When a new threat begins brewing at Hogwarts, and the state of peoples’ lives are at stake, Aralynn must work with her brother and friends to stop it before it’s too late.

Contrition

It was a luminous and rather sweltering mid-summer day in late July. The sun sat high in the sky, casting hot rays unto the tallgrass prairie surrounding a large, misshapen house in the center of it….

Read more…
